data.title: Plays: Gerhart Hauptmann: Before Daybreak, The Weavers, The Beaver Coat by Reinh 9780826407276
data.meta_description: Plays: Gerhart Hauptmann by Reinhold Grimm, Caroline Molina Y. Vedia. Gerhart Hauptmann (1862-1946) is generally considered a pioneer of modern drama. This Nobel Prize-winning author is here represented by three of his best-loved plays.
